{"id": 2185, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于变老之后的生活，你都有哪些忧虑？", "description": "换句话说，你不想成为一个啥样的老年人？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 4702, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180213154527dGOTV1S60hNqUP3z.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-23T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 266752, "content": "求死不得", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269350}, {"id": 266753, "content": "怕得老年痴呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221366}, {"id": 267009, "content": "是否还能像童年一样饭来张口 衣来伸手；像成年后一样有自己的房子，地盘，没人嫌弃你身上的老年味，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905397}, {"id": 267265, "content": "碌碌无为", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271459}, {"id": 267777, "content": "能看到第几代iPhone，不想错事新事物新科技", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642627}, {"id": 266754, "content": "类比“油腻的中年人”，当然是不想变成“油腻的老年人”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260743}, {"id": 266755, "content": "与你只有短短几十年的缘分?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 266756, "content": "后悔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649889}, {"id": 266501, "content": "行动不便，不能旅行\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120872}, {"id": 266758, "content": "需要别人照顾", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269349}, {"id": 266759, "content": "有口臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128178}, {"id": 266760, "content": "不被爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127458}, {"id": 266761, "content": "不能面对生死 没钱。。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269380}, {"id": 267017, "content": "没有特殊严重疾病的情况下，耳朵，关节，眼睛都老化给生活带来困难，给家人带来麻烦的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267472}, {"id": 266762, "content": "害怕孤独，没有地位。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269390}, {"id": 266763, "content": "没钱看病救命", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 266764, "content": "独自一人，不能自理", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269102}, {"id": 267788, "content": "目前不打算要孩子 又怕老了后悔当初的选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662908}, {"id": 266766, "content": "担心跟不上极速发展的社会，无法和孩子们有共同语言交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244500}, {"id": 266767, "content": "老伴走的比我早", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898664}, {"id": 268303, "content": "怕老了以后会腿脚不方便还有驼背", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276228}, {"id": 266768, "content": "死不掉也活不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269414}, {"id": 266513, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572530}, {"id": 266769, "content": "没找到活着的理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216610}, {"id": 268305, "content": "太多挂碍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860055}, {"id": 266770, "content": "我觉得对于基佬来说最大的问题是没有人陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954245}, {"id": 266772, "content": "没伴、没子女", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 266775, "content": "担心自己不够成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269432}, {"id": 267544, "content": "没人，没钱，没脑子……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272769}, {"id": 266777, "content": "我不想成为一个无所事事的老人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711384}, {"id": 266778, "content": "可能会像现在的我们一样，嘲笑（被嘲笑）固执顽固，然后慢慢嫌弃（被嫌弃）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054677}, {"id": 266779, "content": "不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269447}, {"id": 266780, "content": "容颜易老，亲人离世，求生不能，求死不得", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479445}, {"id": 266781, "content": "还能不能过的精彩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269308}, {"id": 268317, "content": "老无所依", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260741}, {"id": 266782, "content": "不想劳累", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258723}, {"id": 267038, "content": "后悔年轻时的选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709240}, {"id": 267039, "content": "和爱的人不在一块", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270403}, {"id": 266784, "content": "没有她", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221791}, {"id": 271648, "content": "孤独与痛苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279383}, {"id": 266785, "content": "因为不会编程而被机器人保姆欺负虐待", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511330}, {"id": 266786, "content": "孤寡老人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269473}, {"id": 266787, "content": "失去清醒的判断力；不能自理；关键时刻不能自主。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258805}, {"id": 266788, "content": "孤老", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269490}, {"id": 266533, "content": "没还完房贷", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897755}, {"id": 266789, "content": "怕自己还是一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266753}, {"id": 267045, "content": "怕坐公交被人让座", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270473}, {"id": 266534, "content": "步履艰辛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104968}, {"id": 266790, "content": "孤独 同代人逐渐离开 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005386}, {"id": 266535, "content": "健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026298}]}